OL,3,CWhat has AQoS axe got to do with
OL,4,Clicence fee deal?
OL,6,GThe BBC's financial woes are no
OL,7,Gsecret. The cuts to local radio, the
OL,8,Gend of the old BBC News Channel and
OL,9,Gthe changes to Newsnight are the
OL,10,Gdirect result of the falling value of
OL,11,Gthe licence fee.
OL,13,FIt is hard for supporters of the BBC
OL,14,Fnot to worry about a death by a
OL,15,Fthousand cuts if this continues.
OL,17,FBut what about the axing of A Question
OL,18,Fof Sport?
