OL,3,CWhat has AQoS axe got to do with
OL,4,Clicence fee deal?
OL,6,FThe BBC's funding difficulties have
OL,7,Fbeen well covered by the quality
OL,8,Fpress, broadcasters and trade websites.
OL,10,FBut by linking the axing of AQoS to
OL,11,Fmoney, the urgency of the situation
OL,12,Fwas brought home to tabloid readers.
OL,14,FResting AQoS gained massive coverage
OL,15,Fcompared to local radio and Newsnight
OL,16,Fcuts.
