OL,3,CWhat has AQoS axe got to do with
OL,4,Clicence fee deal?
OL,6,FThe actual words used by the BBC were
OL,7,Fcareful ` they simply described,
OL,8,Fcorrectly, the situation facing
OL,9,Fcommissioners. Issues like inflation
OL,10,Fin the industry and prioritising
OL,11,Fcommissions that do well on iPlayer.
OL,13,FBut the impression was clear ` if the
OL,14,FBBC does not get more cash soon, more
OL,15,Fhorrible choices will follow.
OL,17,FThink back to the mid-80s and the
OL,18,FBBC's campaign for a rise in the
OL,19,Flicence fee.
