OL,3,CWhat has AQoS axe got to do with
OL,4,Clicence fee deal?
OL,6,FThe decision to abandon afternoon
OL,7,Ftelevision probably didn't save much `
OL,8,Fthe schedule mostly consisted of
OL,9,Ffilms, imports and repeats.
OL,11,FBut the humiliation of seeing endless
OL,12,Fhours of Ceefax on the corporation's
OL,13,Fflagship channel highlighted the grim
OL,14,Ffinancial reality.
OL,16,FCreatively it is the right decision to
OL,17,Frest A Question of Sport.
