OL,3,CWhat has AQoS axe got to do with
OL,4,Clicence fee deal?
OL,6,FPersonally I hope it will return in a
OL,7,Fyear or two in something more like its
OL,8,Fold format ` a game based on sporting
OL,9,Fknowledge, with a presenter in the
OL,10,Ftraditions of David Vine, David
OL,11,FColeman and Sue Barker and not a half-
OL,12,Fbaked comedy show.
OL,14,FBut let's hope the explanation for the
OL,15,Funderlying factors which led to the
OL,16,Fdecision to rest it will help the
OL,17,Fpublic understand that you get what
OL,18,Fyou pay for.
